data.description:
Located in Jacksonville Beach, Southern Swells is a craft brewery and taproom focused on New-England IPAs, Heavily Fruited Sours, Imperial Stouts and Mixed-Fermentation.
 

Southern Swells Brewing Co. opened in January 2017 and has been dedicated to consistently producing high quality craft beers while providing an inviting and friendly taproom experience. 

With over 7500 sq. ft., the brewery and taproom space is vast allowing for groups of all sizes to relax and enjoy our offerings. Our location also features a private events area and an outdoor patio.

Our draft list is constantly changing and features an array of styles with a definite focus on soft, hazy, citrus forward IPAs and Double IPAs.
